{"tid":1597632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[對抗林鄭9up答問大會] 如果真係搞一個全民記者會，應該邀請咩人上去?","createTime":"2019-09-27T04:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T09:42:37.000Z","uid":193471,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e6473f5249c21dfc75c8ad8d905660405d060bce","tid":1597632,"uid":193471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:41:55.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇左個post講全民記者會嘅idea, 聽落同諗落個畫面都好有picture<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後再聽完林鄭個記者會，覺得可能會令到場運動輸，所以一定唔可以笑笑口，笑完就算</span><br />\n<br />\n所以一定要搞得成呢個記者會，邀請所有不同界別嘅人上黎做呢個大宣言<br />\n我個腦就係每個界別都有人上去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不論係泛民, 自決, 獨派, 醫護, 律師, 藝人, 文宣, 衝衝子</span><br />\n人選方面有冇咩好提議?<br />\n<br />\n[十一國殤] 如果真係行得成呢一步，香港人一定唔會再俾人睇死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1596375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1596375</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"888f3b9a90e17bc5f6184184b11135ca92bbbdc2","tid":1597632,"uid":193471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:47:45.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"4ca77542961ec6090af365dee957f9f66fa618a9","tid":1597632,"uid":45991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c09e176014f991ce91e75f9a657e5707f2423a7","tid":1597632,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67602594121546748a9757385e8468e8425092ba","tid":1597632,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"全個政府invite 晒囉<br />\n擇撚晒佢地名"},{"pid":"51b97fc011de3fd9df7e4f8c994b74ff490d6349","tid":1597632,"uid":193471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67602594121546748a9757385e8468e8425092ba","tid":1597632,"uid":5